  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2803930/extras/2f150ed1c590a91113c2029ee69bd4d2.poster.avif?t=1764037447\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2803930/extras/2f150ed1c590a91113c2029ee69bd4d2.webm?t=1764037447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2803930/extras/2f150ed1c590a91113c2029ee69bd4d2.mp4?t=1764037447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In front of you is a workshop with a variety of machines for creating various items. You need to order resources for crafting items to order, and create them using machines in the workshop. For completing tasks, you receive a reward, which you can spend on purchasing new resources for new orders, as well as improving the workshop by purchasing new machines or storage platforms. The controls are simple, you need only press one button - the left mouse button.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2803930/extras/677760a1d0b87bd043f5c4651144d8f1.poster.avif?t=1764037447\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2803930/extras/677760a1d0b87bd043f5c4651144d8f1.webm?t=1764037447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2803930/extras/677760a1d0b87bd043f5c4651144d8f1.mp4?t=1764037447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2803930/extras/2f150ed1c590a91113c2029ee69bd4d2.poster.avif?t=1764037447\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2803930/extras/2f150ed1c590a91113c2029ee69bd4d2.webm?t=1764037447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2803930/extras/2f150ed1c590a91113c2029ee69bd4d2.mp4?t=1764037447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In front of you is a workshop with a variety of machines for creating various items. You need to order resources for crafting items to order, and create them using machines in the workshop. For completing tasks, you receive a reward, which you can spend on purchasing new resources for new orders, as well as improving the workshop by purchasing new machines or storage platforms. The controls are simple, you need only press one button - the left mouse button.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2803930/extras/677760a1d0b87bd043f5c4651144d8f1.poster.avif?t=1764037447\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2803930/extras/677760a1d0b87bd043f5c4651144d8f1.webm?t=1764037447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2803930/extras/677760a1d0b87bd043f5c4651144d8f1.mp4?t=1764037447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
